      "text": [
        "499 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «حَدُّ اَلْقَبْرِ إِلَى اَلتَّرْقُوَةِ»"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.499 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"The depth of the grave is to the collarbone (clavicle).\""
        ]
      }
